<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="originally-adv">originally <strong><em>adv</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /ə'rɪdʒənəli/    美 /ə'rɪdʒənəli/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>起初；原来：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The store was originally quite small.
这家商店原来非常小。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Originally, we had planned a tour of Scotland, but we didn’t go in the end.
起先，我们计划到苏格兰旅游，但最后没有成行。</p></div></div>